php-barcode needs an external programm for encodings other then EAN/ISBN<BR>
<ul>
<li>download gnu-barcode from <a href="http://www.gnu.org/software/barcode/">www.gnu.org/software/barcode/</a></li>
<li>compile and install them</li>
<li>download genbarcode from <a href="http://www.ashberg.de/php-barcode/">www.ashberg.de/php-barcode/</a></li>
<li>compile and install them</li>
<li>specify path to genbarcode in php-barcode.php</li>
</ul>
